        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="verdana, Arial" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:700; margin-top:30px !important">One Year of Conflict in the Middle East</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopolitics.world/email/images/gp-oct-7-1.jpg" alt="One Year of Conflict in the Middle East" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="verdana, Arial" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Avenir Next',Avenir,'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Ubuntu,Roboto,Noto,'Segoe ui',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;">Today marks one year since Hamas launched the attack on Israel, which resulted in over a thousand deaths and hundreds of kidnappings. Since then, tens of thousands have died in the <a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/oct-7-tens-thousands-dead-forever-war-rcna166765" target="_blank">ongoing conflict</a>, and over a hundred hostages remain unreturned. Hopes for peace have significantly diminished; Israel remains angered and shaken, with families of hostages suffering deeply, while Gaza faces a humanitarian disaster due to intense bombing.</p>
          <p style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Avenir Next',Avenir,'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Ubuntu,Roboto,Noto,'Segoe ui',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;">The situation in the Middle East <a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/10/06/nx-s1-5142440/israeli-gaza-lebanon-oct-7" target="_blank">continues to escalate</a>, with increased attacks between Israel and Iranian-backed proxy groups. Countries like Egypt and <a href="https://thehill.com/opinion/international/4603890-why-jordan-came-to-israels-rescue/" target="_blank">Jordan</a>, which have formal relationships with Israel, are facing growing discontent among their populations, making peace efforts increasingly difficult. Neither of these nations nor any of Israel’s Western allies have successfully developed a viable peace plan. These conflicts have led to significant political polarization in the West, with a notable rise in <a href="https://www.voanews.com/a/antisemitism-islamophobia-surge-in-2023-watchdogs-say/7407451.html" target="_blank">antisemitic and Islamophobic incidents.</a></p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <!-- Content sections -->
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
